  "_integrationTestNotes": "Integration tests should verify: (1) Activity_0mmcuzy (Analyze receipt) calls real AI/OCR service; (2) Activity_17krtpn (Identify damage in photo) calls real computer vision service; (3) Activity_0etxz4e calls real CRM/policy system for customer and policy data; (4) Activity_100o6io DMN evaluates real business rules; (5) Activity_0ankyj2 triggers real payment process integration. Note: correlationKey for banking_info_received is the ticketId (as a string)."
